Interface OWLOntologyStorer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractOWLOntologyStorer, DLSyntaxHTMLOntologyStorer, DLSyntaxOntologyStorer, DLSyntaxOntologyStorerBase, KRSS2OWLSyntaxOntologyStorer, KRSS2SyntaxOntologyStorer, KRSSSyntaxOntologyStorer, LatexOntologyStorer, ManchesterOWLSyntaxOntologyStorer, OBOFlatFileOntologyStorer, OWLFunctionalSyntaxOntologyStorer, OWLTutorialSyntaxOntologyStorer, OWLXMLOntologyStorer, RDFXMLOntologyStorer, TurtleOntologyStorer

    public interface OWLOntologyStorer
extends java.io.Serializable
    Author: Matthew Horridge
    The University Of Manchester
    Bio-Health Informatics Group
    Date: 02-Jan-2007

    An ontology storer stores an ontology in a particular format at a location specified by a particular URI.
